criteria.textblock:
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  medical diagnosis of CP;

          -  levels I to IV according to the GMFCS;

          -  levels I to III according to MACS.

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  presence of surgery or a chemical neuromuscular blockade in the upper limbs within six
             months prior to participation in the study;

          -  lack of comprehension of the experimental instructions.
